# 📌 Text Classification with Transformers

## 🚀 Overview

This notebook shows how to use  `transformers` sentiment analysis on the IMDB dataset. It covers data loading, preprocessing, training, and evaluation.

## 🛠️ Setup

Install dependencies:

```sh
pip install transformers datasets evaluate
```

## 📂 Dataset

Uses the IMDB dataset with movie reviews labeled as positive/negative:

```python
from datasets import load_dataset
imdb = load_dataset("imdb")
```

## 🔍 Steps

1️⃣ Install dependencies\
2️⃣ Load & preprocess data\
3️⃣ Train a model\
4️⃣ Evaluate performance

## ▶️ Run the Notebook

Execute the cells in Jupyter or Colab (enable GPU for better performance!).

